name: UnofficialFoursquareRestaurantGuide
0:
”Alexa, ask four square, what are the trending restaurants near San Francisco”
”Alexa, open four square and get trending restaurants near San Francisco”
”Alexa, trending restaurants near San Francisco from four square”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: four square
des: Get information about trending restaurants in your area. After hearing the list of restaurants you can say "More" to list more restaurants or "Number 1" to get more information about the first restaurant that was listed. Additional commands will be listed after each response.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
